01:41.234 --> 01:42.568
Hey, trev, what's happening?

01:43.536 --> 01:44.703
It's Ashley.

01:45.472 --> 01:46.605
Douglas.

01:47.607 --> 01:49.274
You wanna come over
to my mom's house?

01:51.377 --> 01:52.711
Well, it's kinda like a party.

01:52.713 --> 01:54.313
Just a couple of people,
not too much.

01:55.348 --> 01:56.615
