27:06.726 --> 27:08.592
Which one has
the most compartments?

27:08.594 --> 27:10.527
Compartments, as in how?

27:10.529 --> 27:12.229
I'm gonna have a lot
of supplies, and pencils,

27:12.231 --> 27:13.430
so I need some compartments.

27:13.432 --> 27:15.699
Okay, so you need room.

27:15.701 --> 27:17.735
Well, this...
This larger bag,

27:18.470 --> 27:20.104
it's a pretty dynamic bag.

27:20.106 --> 27:23.073
It's got the adjustable
safety wires,

27:24.275 --> 27:25.342
shoulder straps...

27:25.344 --> 27:27.144
That's a coin purse.

27:27.146 --> 27:31.115
It's got a good base,
can fit books, notebooks,

27:31.117 --> 27:32.316
laptop computer.

27:33.685 --> 27:35.552
You're welcome to try it on,
if you want.

27:35.554 --> 27:37.521
People buy this bag,
like teachers?

27:37.523 --> 27:39.123
Oh, of course, all the time.

27:39.125 --> 27:40.424
Teachers, students,

27:40.426 --> 27:42.092
professors, athletes.

27:42.627 --> 27:43.761
Try it on.

27:47.632 --> 27:48.766
How does that feel?

27:49.467 --> 27:51.101
- Yeah, feels nice.
- Feels nice?

27:51.603 --> 27:53.137
Yeah.

27:53.139 --> 27:55.239
- All right. Good luck.
- Thank you.

28:32.178 --> 28:33.243
Stop!

28:33.245 --> 28:34.311
Ashley!

28:34.313 --> 28:36.380
Why you gotta do that?

28:36.382 --> 28:37.848
I'm sorry. I'm sorry...

28:38.416 --> 28:39.483
Hey.

28:39.485 --> 28:40.584
Yeah.

28:40.586 --> 28:42.252
I thought you'd be done
a while ago.

28:42.254 --> 28:43.287
Uh-uh. And you know

28:43.289 --> 28:45.289
you don't have to
wait around for me, right?

28:45.291 --> 28:46.323
Yes, I do.

28:46.325 --> 28:48.726
Somebody's gotta, you know,
watch your back.

28:48.728 --> 28:49.860
Oh, from that dude?

28:49.862 --> 28:52.362
Uh-uh. Come on. Let's go.

28:52.364 --> 28:53.764
- You know what I think?
- Hmm?

28:53.766 --> 28:55.933
I think taco man
really likes you.

28:55.935 --> 28:57.501
What makes you say that?

28:57.503 --> 28:59.169
You've been
wearing him out lately.

28:59.171 --> 29:01.605
Yeah, well,
he manages the hotel.

29:01.607 --> 29:02.973
- Oh, really?
- Mm-hmm.

29:06.244 --> 29:08.812
Think he got some refrigerators
he might want to get rid of?

29:09.414 --> 29:10.681
I don't know.

29:10.683 --> 29:12.983
He does have one of them
small ones, you know.

29:12.985 --> 29:15.219
Small ones got the freon
in them too, don't they?

29:16.187 --> 29:17.521
Ask him for me.

29:17.523 --> 29:18.956
Well, what you got going on?

29:18.958 --> 29:20.390
Oh, I'm headed to this class.

29:20.392 --> 29:22.159
- Oh, okay. -You wanna
take this to the house?

29:22.161 --> 29:23.227
Yeah. Sure.

29:23.229 --> 29:24.361
See you later on tonight.

29:24.363 --> 29:26.196
- I don't know.
- -I don't know!

29:26.198 --> 29:29.032
I might have something going
on, I'll let you know later.

29:29.034 --> 29:30.534
All right, come on,
people know me here.

29:30.536 --> 29:31.869
All right, I'm late.

29:31.871 --> 29:33.570
I'll see you later tonight
or else.

29:33.572 --> 29:34.638
Or else what?

29:34.640 --> 29:35.806
I'll think of something.

29:35.808 --> 29:37.307
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

29:37.976 --> 29:39.042
Bye!

30:12.110 --> 30:13.110
Pittman?

30:13.812 --> 30:15.078
Jeremy pittman?

30:18.183 --> 30:19.650
<i>How are you feeling?</i>

30:19.652 --> 30:20.951
