30:20.953 --> 30:23.220
Good, do you need anything?
Some water, or snacks?

30:23.222 --> 30:24.388
Sure!

30:24.390 --> 30:25.656
What would you like?

30:25.658 --> 30:26.790
I don't know, like...

30:26.792 --> 30:27.891
Steak and fries?

30:27.893 --> 30:30.127
Oh, yeah.
Coming right up.

30:30.129 --> 30:32.663
Hey, Tammy, we would like
a fillet mignon,

30:32.665 --> 30:34.097
and a side order of fries.

30:36.201 --> 30:37.201
So...

30:38.036 --> 30:40.070
Now tell me, are you having

30:40.072 --> 30:42.439
any adverse side effects
to your patches?

30:42.441 --> 30:43.774
No, ma'am, nothing adverse.

30:43.776 --> 30:45.309
I do have a question, though.

30:45.311 --> 30:46.276
Go ahead.

30:46.278 --> 30:48.412
My friend Ashley said
he know a guy

30:48.414 --> 30:50.714
that can control his body
temperature by holding his breath.

30:50.716 --> 30:51.949
Is that possible?

30:51.951 --> 30:54.551
Well, I haven't researched
that, Mr. pittman,

30:54.553 --> 30:56.286
but I'll look into that, okay?

30:57.455 --> 30:59.022
Let's see... breath...

30:59.524 --> 31:00.958
I'll let you know.

31:00.960 --> 31:02.993
Um, now, what I want to do,

31:02.995 --> 31:05.128
