wearing four patches?

31:17.675 --> 31:19.409
Well, Jeremy,

31:19.411 --> 31:21.745
we find you a particularly

31:21.747 --> 31:23.881
meaningful subject
for our purposes.

31:23.883 --> 31:25.215
What do you mean?

31:25.217 --> 31:28.619
It's rare for a male
of your age, race

31:28.621 --> 31:29.987
and economic status

31:29.989 --> 31:32.422
