at our offices.

31:32.657 --> 31:33.957
It is.

31:33.959 --> 31:36.126
Dr. merton, you care
about me, right?

31:37.562 --> 31:38.595
Let me be honest.

31:40.365 --> 31:41.565
Some of the results

31:41.567 --> 31:43.567
