31:46.805 --> 31:48.405
What's in it for me?

31:48.407 --> 31:49.439
Well, naturally, we would

31:49.441 --> 31:51.842
double the amount
of money you receive.

31:51.844 --> 31:53.810
Can I still go swimming
with the patches on?

31:53.812 --> 31:55.979
Yes, you can go swimming
with the patches on.

31:55.981 --> 31:58.515
Just keep living your life
the way you normally would.

31:58.517 --> 31:58.515
All right.

31:58.517 --> 32:01.351
