in one of these rooms.</i>

32:12.363 --> 32:14.431
I'm sorry the desks
are so small.

32:14.433 --> 32:15.999
Aw, these desks are cool.

32:17.869 --> 32:19.870
Let me see
if I can still fit in them.

32:20.805 --> 32:22.472
Yeah. Here you go.

32:24.175 --> 32:26.443
Mr. Carlos, how long
do you think this will take?

32:26.445 --> 32:28.245
Jeremy said you were
really good at this.

32:28.947 --> 32:30.047
Well, that depends.

32:30.049 --> 32:31.982
