Yeah, not in cursive.

33:23.235 --> 33:24.601
No, no, no.
Regular is fine.

33:24.603 --> 33:26.036
Yeah, I can do that, I mean,

33:26.038 --> 33:28.372
- can I use the chalk and board...
- Sure.

33:40.284 --> 33:42.319
Does that look right? 'Cause
