Oh...

55:19.115 --> 55:20.382
Hello?

55:21.518 --> 55:22.518
Yes.

55:24.888 --> 55:26.622
Yeah, I know the street.

55:27.924 --> 55:28.957
Okay.

55:29.826 --> 55:31.093
Yeah, yeah, we know...

55:31.095 --> 55:32.361
Just give us 20 minutes.

55:32.363 --> 55:33.896
We'll be right there.

55:33.898 --> 55:34.863
All right.

55:34.865 --> 55:36.432
Right... no, thank you.

55:37.835 --> 55:39.134
We got a fridge?

